Sentencas: Gadolinia-doped ceria (GDC) is widely used as an interlayer for preventing the formation of SrZrO3 between yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte and lanthanum strontium cobalt iron oxides (LSCF) cathode for solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Lanthanum-doped ceria interlayer between electrolyte and cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: However, the diffusion of Gd ions to YSZ electrolyte results in the decrease in ionic conductivity due to the formation of Gd-2(Zr, Ce)(2)O-7.
Titulo: Lanthanum-doped ceria interlayer between electrolyte and cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In the present work, we focus on lanthanum-doped ceria (LDC) as an interlayer between YSZ electrolyte and LSCF cathode.
Titulo: Lanthanum-doped ceria interlayer between electrolyte and cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The ionic conductivity of YSZ/LDC composite was higher than that of YSZ/GDC composite in spite of the lower conductivity of LDC than GDC.
Titulo: Lanthanum-doped ceria interlayer between electrolyte and cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The maximum power density for the microtubular SOFC with LDC interlayer was better than that with GDC interlayer.
Titulo: Lanthanum-doped ceria interlayer between electrolyte and cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: While the ohmic resistance decreased by the change from GDC to LDC interlayers, the polarization resistance for oxygen reduction reaction slightly increased as a result of distribution of relaxation times (DRT) analysis.
Titulo: Lanthanum-doped ceria interlayer between electrolyte and cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The chemical compositions of Zr, Ce and La was gradually varied at the interface between YSZ electrolyte and LDC interlayer, which affected the both of ohmic and polarization resistances.
Titulo: Lanthanum-doped ceria interlayer between electrolyte and cathode for solid oxide fuel cells
